khatta meetha ( english : sour and sweet ) is a 2010 hindi comedy drama film written and directed by priyadarshan that stars akshay kumar and trisha krishnan in the lead roles . the film is a remake of priyadarshan 's previous malayalam film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; nadu ( 1988 ) , scripted by sreenivasan . the film was produced by shree ashtavinayak cine vision ltd and hari om productions . it was released on 5 august 2010 .